{"tid":1678384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼同分化好易睇，任何剩係抹黑而完全舉唔出任何理據或合邏輯既理由既，就一定係鬼同搞分化！","createTime":"2019-10-27T15:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T10:27:40.000Z","uid":241151,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"97b7623cc5b1822876382e081eeae84dff503168","tid":1678384,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"求其一句：<br />\n你係五毛 <br />\n乜sir物sir <br />\n拉 <br />\n不推文回覆 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求其講一句就當自己係正義化身可以亂咁抹黑？你當人傻架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733cf30c874532130960581a2404380433febdf5","tid":1678384,"uid":215876,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"點解你咁執著用依個名嘅<br />\n<br />\n拉<br />\n起底<br />\n不推文"},{"pid":"cb28a42916abeec1d65c740c1daace35bc969e65","tid":1678384,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:50:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4ZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=c141d001\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4ZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=55a92c79\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4ZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=ca00b862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"726725b17a9a409a3438c5f2e3adbcd412b19522","tid":1678384,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"733cf30c874532130960581a2404380433febdf5","tid":1678384,"uid":215876,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"點解你咁執著用依個名嘅<br />\n<br />\n拉<br />\n起底<br />\n不推文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"你班人硬係咁興入去人地既post度夾硬問人問題而永遠唔因應主題作出回答，討論或者有理據既反駁，只會入黎留d冇意義既口號黎抹黑<br />\n<br />\n所有人可以留意吓，維穩派多數都係咁"},{"pid":"f0d583fa6cd632865a2c513d597ac23331202f41","tid":1678384,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyT